name: CUE! Characters
description:
All of the Idols from the anime, and defunct game Cue!

For Triggers please look at the samples for specific ones, but generally is the name. A few need the eye color listed too(I tried to put those in the keyword section).

Not all the words are needed that I used in the examples I just didn't narrow down the amount as I had 16 loras to do test. This is especially true in some of the earlier ones I did as I remade 5 of them, and just used prompts I already had for the unreleased test lora that needed heavier prompting.

Also most of them you can easily change hairstyles, and lengths. If it doesn't want to work lower the weight.

These were all trained on NAI, and the samples are from NAI. Weight that I found that works are from .45 to 9. For the idol outfits to show up properly need higher weight generally .8 to 1,.

Tendo Yuuki , and Eniwa Airi sometimes are rendered looking older. I honestly don't know why. Airi is also the hardest one to prompt for as the images available were not that great, and is also the only one I know that needs the hair color specified as when doing test images she popped a few out as blonde.

The loras were trained on 15-20 epocs depending on how many training images I had.
